---
import sandra from '../img/sandra.jpg';
const features = [
  {
    title: "Innovación",
    description: "Siempre busco nuevas formas de resolver problemas y crear experiencias únicas.",
    icon: "bulb"
  },
  {
    title: "Precisión",
    description: "Cada pixel cuenta. Me obsesiono con los detalles para entregar excelencia.",
    icon: "target"
  },
  {
    title: "Colaboración",
    description: "Trabajo codo a codo contigo para transformar tus ideas en realidad.",
    icon: "users"
  },
  {
    title: "Calidad",
    description: "Código limpio, escalable y optimizado para el mejor rendimiento.",
    icon: "shield"
  }
];
---

<section id="about-me-section" class="py-16 md:py-32 bg-[#031605] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Text Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <span class="text-lime text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4">Sobre Mí</span>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light leading-tight tracking-tight uppercase text-[#E8E4DC]">
            Más que diseño, <br />
            <span class="text-[rgba(224,204,250,1)] italic font-light">belleza solida.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-white/70 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Siempre me ha atraído lo bonito.
            La armonía. El equilibrio. Ese detalle que casi nadie percibe… pero que lo cambia todo.

            Con el tiempo entendí algo importante:
            la estética por sí sola no basta.

            Lo verdaderamente potente ocurre cuando la belleza descansa sobre una estructura firme.
            Cuando lo visual emociona… y lo técnico sostiene.

            Trabajo uniendo visión estratégica y ejecución precisa.
            Soy directa, cercana y exigente conmigo misma.
          </p>
          <p>
            No entrego algo “correcto”.
            Entrego algo terminado.

            Para mí, el lujo no tiene que ver con exceso.
            Tiene que ver con criterio.

            Calidad sin ruido.
            Precisión sin espectáculo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6">
          {features.map((feature) => (
            <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 hover:border-lime/30 transition-colors group">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-lime/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-lime group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                {feature.icon === 'bulb' && <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>}
                {feature.icon === 'target' && <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>} <!-- Replacing target with lightning/action based on 'action' look or keep target -->
                {feature.icon === 'users' && <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>}
                {feature.icon === 'shield' && <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>}
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">{feature.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">{feature.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Image & Stats -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-white/5 border border-white/10 group">
            <!-- User Image -->
            <img 
              src={sandra.src} 
              alt="Sandra" 
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            />
            <!-- Overlay Gradient -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-deep-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>

            <!-- Floating Stats Cards -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
                <!-- Stat 1 -->
                <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4 transform translate-y-2 opacity-90 hover:scale-105 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime text-deep-black flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
                        +10
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg leading-none uppercase">Años</p>
                        <p class="text-[rgba(224,204,250,1)] text-[10px] font-bold uppercase">de experiencia</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                 <!-- Stat 2 -->
                 <div class="bg-deep-black/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-3 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all ml-12">
                     <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-lime text-deep-black flex items-center justify-center relative">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-lime animate-ping opacity-20"></div>
                        <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-deep-black rounded-full"></div>
                     </div>
                     <div>
                         <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm leading-none uppercase">Disponibilidad</p>
                         <p class="text-[rgba(224,204,250,1)] text-[10px] font-bold uppercase">Inmediata</p>
                     </div>
                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Decorative Elements -->
        <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-lime/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
